CallCtrAgentFavTrfrDestShare.name: CallCtrAgentFavTrfrDestShare
CallCtrAgentFavTrfrDestShare.description: Represents a sharing entry on a favorite transfer destination in the Omni-Channel softphone for voice call transfers. This object is available in API version 55.0 and later.

ParentId.description: The unique ID of the parent object.

RowCause.description: Reason that this sharing entry exists. If you’re creating a sharing entry, the only permitted value is Manual. If no value is specified, the field defaults to Manual. All other RowCause values are read-only. After the sharing entry is created, this field can’t be edited.

UserOrGroupId.description: The unique ID of the User or Group that has been given access to the favorite transfer destination.
